{"type": "article", "id": 5580, "title": "餐巾环 Napkin Zoo", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-27T07:42:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234020FSjo5Eq4Bmag1ckn.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自以色列特拉维夫的设计工作室 Wishlist 日前为以色列家居用品品牌 Ototo 设计了一款充满童趣的作品餐巾环 Napkin Zoo，将餐巾环的轮廓变成了兔子、熊以及鹿的耳朵，勾勒出一种极富森林风格的用餐环境，亦非常适合有小朋友的家庭使用。这是 Ototo 2015 冬季新品中的一款，6 个装定价 19.99 美元（约合人民币 124 元），<a href=\"http://www.animicausa.com/shop/Napkin-Zoo-Napkin-Rings/tpflypage.tpl.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234018Q3CHwoxTtsADfzIY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523401814mFDBIwaJOsLh8q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052340197cValr9M1wKjUniH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234019SDVsadpbF01Mzk6U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7296875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}